<%= render "shared/page_title", title: "Import Stock Data" %>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
    
    <p>
      Please note that this feature is only to be used in the event of the database becoming corrupt. 
      Prior to using this feature, please ensure that the stock and sent stock tables has been completely
      wiped of all exisiting data, and that the upload file contains the most recent version of your 
      stock data export. Note that this is seperate from the computer life-cycle data importer. 
    </p>
    <h4>
      <%= form_tag import_stocks_path, multipart: true do %>
        <%= file_field_tag :file %>
        <%= submit_tag "Import" %>
      <% end %>
    </h4>
    
  </div>
</div>